show.title: Madam, Your CEO Husband Will Save Your Village
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/CSLnPT
show.description: He’s actually a powerful CEO—living in disguise as a security guard for reasons only he knows. Just as fate would have it, a bold young woman arrives to protect a village… and unknowingly, his heart. A heartwarming tale of secrets, destiny, and a romance that asks: will their bond lead to marriage?
